
Notification for Mac OS X
=========================

Usage
-----

Using window
~~~~~~~~~~~~

This application has a window including some textfields.

- Title: is used as the title of a notification
- Subtitle: is used as the subtitle of a notification
- Body: is used as the body text of a notification
- Delay: specifies x seconds; a notification shows after x seconds

Using console arguments
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This application is able to be used on Terminal with open command::

    $ open -g $APP_PATH/Notification.app --args \
        -title="This is a title" \
        -subtitle "This is a subtitle" \
        -body "This is a body text" \
        -delay 3


